[I] A parser for a MIME tree and is based on KMime

[T] A parser for a MIME tree and is based on KMime. The goal is given a MIME
[T] tree to extract a list of parts (e.g. text, html) and a list of
[T] attachments, check the validity of the signatures and decrypt any
[T] encrypted part.

[U] https://invent.kde.org/pim/mimetreeparser

